  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A prospective, observational study will be performed measuring recirculation of blood through
      a veno-venous Extracoporeal Membrane Oxygenation (vvECMO) in patients with acute respiratory
      distress syndrome (ARDS) on vvECMO. ECMO blood flow will be adjusted with respect to
      recirculation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
